profile:
United Roofing & Exteriors is a family run business with over 50 years of combined experience. We base our business on support and trust. Home and business owners should feel comfortable with a superior roof over their head without the worry of a large financial burden. As roofing experts, we pay close attention to detail and only use high quality materials. We will always take special care to maintain your exterior property while performing our services.

We specialize in:

Euroshield® Environmentally Friendly Roofing
Euroshield® Rubber Roofing
Our goal is to build long-lasting relationships with our clients. We provide services that will exceed your expectations, and look forward to planning your next roofing or exterior project with you.
